RVU Information Tables

Source: R/tables.R
link_tables.Rd

RVU Information Tables

Usage

rvu_link_table(years)

rvu_zip_links(years)

conversion_factor(dos)

Arguments

years

<int> RVU source file year

dos

<Date> Date of Service, in the form YYYY-MM-DD

Value

<tibble> containing RVU information

Examples
